        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down. | Bromley. | Kent. S.E.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>Oct. 25<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></date>
                    <salute>My dear Lindley</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I am infinitely obliged for your letter, answering everything so clearly &amp; so fully.—<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p>
<p>Do <hi rend="doubleUnderline">not</hi> read enclosed without you like, I send it on mere <hi rend="underline">chance</hi> of being new to you.—</p>
<p>I sh<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. be most grateful for <hi rend="underline">any</hi> orchids (especially Dendrobium) in flower &amp; <hi rend="doubleUnderline">bud</hi> : if it be a small parcel <hi rend="underline">tin cannister</hi> best way by <hi rend="underline">Post</hi>, &amp; you must let me repay postage: if too large, address.</p> 
<figure type="diagram"> 
<p>C. Darwin | care of Down Postman | Bromley | <hi rend="doubleUnderline">Kent</hi> per Railway</p> </figure> 
<p>I terribly want any one of your “Arethuseæ.”<ref target="#foot.f3"/></p>
<p>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> James Veitch has been <hi rend="underline">most</hi> generous;<ref target="#foot.f4"/> I did not know that you had spoken to him: if you see him pray say I am truly grateful. I dare not write to a live Bishop or a Lady;<ref target="#foot.f5"/> but if I knew the address of “Rucker”?? &amp; might use your name as introduction I would write.<ref target="#foot.f6"/> I am half mad on subject.— Hooker has sent me many exotics; but I stopped him, for I thought I sh<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. make a fool of myself; but since I have determined to publish, I much regret it.</p>
<p>I will not trouble you for the Books, for systematic works are out of my line.—</p>
<p>Hooker is trying to buy Reichenbach on the pollen &amp; if he gets it will lend me, for it is in no public Library &amp; I do not suppose would be worth my buying.<ref target="#foot.f7"/></p>
<p>With cordial thanks for your great kindness.—</p>
<p>Yours very sincerely | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
